column1: Hospital Name: Providence Kodiak Island Medical Center
Chargemaster for CMS Pricing Transparency - Procedures
Hospital Charges include hospital services, pharmaceuticals and supply items necessary to treat patients.
This is a snapshot of the Chargemaster at a point in time, and is subject to change.
These items are represented on separate tabs.
Supply prices may vary based on manufacturer's cost to hospital.
Drug prices may vary based on dosage, supplier's availability and cost to hospital.
